https://chicago.suntimes.com/news/aclu-demands-removal-children-dcfs-care-aurora-chicago-lakeshore-hospital/amp/

Previously, in 2011 this hospital was cited for poor staffing, lax oversight, and rape occurring at the facility <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/lifestyles/health/ct-met-lakeshore-hospital-report-20110517-story.html|title=Report faults care of young psychiatric patients at Chicago Lakeshore Hospital|first=David Jackson, Tribune|last=reporter|website=chicagotribune.com}}</ref>

Chicago Lakeshore Hospital opened its children's psychiatric center in 2013z <ref name="dnainfo">{{cite web|url=http://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20130211/uptown/chicago-lakeshore-hospital-open-childrens-psychiatric-center-uptown|title=Chicago Lakeshore Hospital to Open Children's Psychiatric Center in Uptown - Uptown - DNAinfo.com Chicago|publisher=dnainfo.com|accessdate=2014-04-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424194055/http://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20130211/uptown/chicago-lakeshore-hospital-open-childrens-psychiatric-center-uptown|archivedate=2014-04-24|df=}}</ref>

